data.description: Country living at its best in this charming brick ranch! Less than 10 minutes to get to the freeway or town, you can enjoy all that country life has to offer yet still be able to have all of the conveniences of town. Mini farm life dreams coming true with 2.6 acres & enough room to have a couple of horses, cows, goats or sheep. House offers 3 spacious bedrooms with a full unfinished walk out basement w/ the possibility to finish and expand. Oversized one car garage for extra storage as well a barn big enough for three stalls. Plenty of room to park your RV or build another garage and/or work shop. Endless possibilities with a great price tag!
